# 懵然不知

(pos: 形容詞)
<explanation>
yue: 懵 (mang2) 同 然 (ran4) 同聲，但讀作 mung2。係人突然唔知咩意思，或係對咩事完全唔清楚嘅狀態。
eng: completely unaware; in a state of stupor.

<eg>
yue: 佢哋入咗咁多嘢，佢哋好懵然不知。 (wo1 zai1 dou1 dou1 dou1 dou1 dou1, zoi1 zoi1 zoi1 zoi1 zoi1 zung2 mung2 mung2 zung2.)
eng: They have eaten so much that they are completely unaware.

<eg>
yue: 佢好懵然不知，好似個傻仔。 (zoi1 zung2 mung2 mung2 zung2, zoi1 zung2 zung2 zung2 zung2 zung2.)
eng: He is completely unaware, like a silly child. [end of text]


